The paper discusses the hardware realization of rectenna circuits and practical techniques for achieving simultaneous wireless information and power transfer (SWIPT) in the domains of time, power, antennas, and space. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Electromagnetics (cs.EM), Systems and Control (cs.SY), or Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
